Class KeyValueTableModel<RecordType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • xal.extension.widgets.swing.KeyValueTableModel<RecordType>

    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    KeyValueFilteredTableModel

    public class KeyValueTableModel<RecordType>
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
    Table Model whose records are arbitrary objects and whose values are obtained through the Key-Value adaptor
